# MQC Implementation Plan

## Overview

Implement the MQC (Merkle Quantum Connect) protocol as a standalone
library in `socket-level-wrapper-MQC/`. This replaces TLS 1.3 + X.509
with a pure post-quantum protocol using ML-KEM key exchange, ML-DSA-87
signed authentication, and Merkle tree proof verification.

See `README-MQC-specifications.md` for the full protocol specification.

